ActOrder in Council P.C. 2007-281 of March 2, 2007
PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 2021-703 of July 1, 2021, by replacing “for a term of two years” with “for a term of three years”; and designation of NORA KATHLEEN SPINKS, a member of the National Seniors Council, to be Chairperson of the National Seniors Council, on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending on June 30, 2024, effective December 14, 2022.
